5. Accept the price from user. Ask the user if he is a student (user may say y or n). If he is a student and he has purchased more than 500 then discount is 20%, otherwise discount is 10%. But if he is not a student then if he has purchased more than 600, discount is 15%, otherwise there is no discount.
